[
  "Francesco Gaetano Caltagirone is the president of Caltagirone, a holding company with interests in construction, cement, real estate, finance and publishing.",
  "His family, which hails from Sicily, was in the construction and real estate business, which he expanded and took into other sectors. ",
  "In 1999, after buying several papers, he built media group Caltagirone Editore, Italy's sixth largest newspaper publisher.",
  "The bulk of his wealth is now stakes in two publicly traded firms: insurance company Assicurazioni Generali and cement giant Cementir. "
]